                "date": "2009-11-02T00:00:00Z",
                "journal": "Batch Effects and Noise in Microarray Experiments: Sources and Solutions",
                "title": "Principal Variance Components Analysis: Estimating Batch Effects in Microarray Gene Expression Data"
            },
